summary: I have a new dungeon im adding that\\\'s currently a WIP, and need a few people to test it out.
descriptionHtml:
Hi guys, just a quick description here. I\'ve got a dungeon that im creating as part of a quest and armor mod, but i\\\'ve run into a few snags. When i COC from the main menu, everything\\\'s working fine. 

But when i use an existing character, its buggy. So i need a few people to DL the dungeon and COC to it on a character they have, and make sure its working correctly.


-------------------------------
Things im looking for
-------------------------------

-Do potions spawn
-Does armor spawn
-Do draugr ambushes spawn
-Do any followers port in with you


You will be ported upon the COC command to an area right before an ambush and with a few potions and leveled spawns.

COC 01gravuunheim


Thanks you, and i appreciate your help. Anyone who helps will be credited when the mod is finalized.

-PK
